{"id": 3020, "genre": 1001, "title": "在不考虑难度的前提下，你都给生活设定过哪些「plan B」？", "description": "一些「虽然未必能实现，但总会忍不住暗中规划」的小想法。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 1742, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190929223051lHu2DeBw7sQ5GV4x.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-03T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 347907, "content": "立刻辞职", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665454}, {"id": 347908, "content": "去到每一个城市工作一段时间，赚点钱再把这个城市好好玩一遍。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620576}, {"id": 347909, "content": "走进一座树木繁茂的大山。\n自己建一座道观，\n不问世事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424867}, {"id": 347910, "content": "没有选择", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665465}, {"id": 347912, "content": "现代游牧生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1611164}, {"id": 347914, "content": "嫖娼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665484}, {"id": 347915, "content": "gap year", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1546422}, {"id": 347916, "content": "一路流浪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460561}, {"id": 347917, "content": "planA都没想好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637308}, {"id": 348173, "content": "环游世界 用相机记录世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666244}, {"id": 347920, "content": "环球旅行\n找一个契合的伴侣一起过着自由旅行的生活 一辈子居无定所 就到处走 看世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665508}, {"id": 347922, "content": "自律人士", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1444167}, {"id": 347923, "content": "非洲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 347926, "content": "世界和平", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1663976}, {"id": 347927, "content": "读博", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 77633}, {"id": 347931, "content": "环游世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603901}, {"id": 347933, "content": "我想让自己在遇到事情的时候不困难，父母健康，家庭和睦，有一个通情达理的妻子，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883319}, {"id": 347934, "content": "攒钱出国读研然后移民", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665528}, {"id": 347935, "content": "减肥减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665529}, {"id": 349216, "content": "当艺术家而不是科学家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437091}, {"id": 347938, "content": "做个温柔的男孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665536}, {"id": 347939, "content": "很多人想过把某个业余爱好当成主业的plan B吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 347941, "content": "开一条美食节", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665539}, {"id": 347686, "content": "备胎", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103045}, {"id": 347942, "content": "考博士", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619862}, {"id": 347687, "content": "从商，稳定以后开家清吧，不求赚钱，晚上过去弹琴唱歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647557}, {"id": 347688, "content": "当个小说家", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283379}, {"id": 347944, "content": "拥有一家影院，放映自己认为有价值的电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664869}, {"id": 347689, "content": "考博", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773145}, {"id": 347945, "content": "独自一人，开着车，行驶在草原上", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665544}, {"id": 347690, "content": "单身一辈子", "image": null, "praise_count": 204, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1659809}, {"id": 347946, "content": "坐不到车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1663842}, {"id": 347691, "content": "无牵无挂后，找个没人的地方过瓦尔登式的生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 234, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1651671}, {"id": 347948, "content": "有房 有存款 有老婆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484371}, {"id": 347693, "content": "在西藏一个小村庄，开家杂货铺", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647923}, {"id": 347949, "content": "有财富有健康是人生最大的底气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641739}, {"id": 347694, "content": "买一所有落地窗户的大房子/ 成败一片果园/ 橘子葡萄李子都来一点/ 然后过着冬天红薯夏天西瓜的日子", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871118}, {"id": 347695, "content": "一夜暴富，然后……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373628}, {"id": 347696, "content": "当个背包客，无牵无挂地环游全世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 130, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618569}, {"id": 347952, "content": "有车有房有票子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665554}, {"id": 347697, "content": "当一名教授哈哈哈哈。", "image": "img/option/option/20191004080250FUHVPcBQgEMdX4OS", "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291669}, {"id": 347698, "content": "66号公路到纽约", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665111}, {"id": 347699, "content": "减肥减肥减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664992}, {"id": 347700, "content": "移民", "image": null, "praise_count": 197, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424722}, {"id": 347701, "content": "BE THE GOAT", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662305}, {"id": 347704, "content": "放弃事业，去流浪，做个自私且平庸的流浪汉", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665016}, {"id": 347962, "content": "环游世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665570}, {"id": 347708, "content": "去冰岛定居", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665072}, {"id": 347964, "content": "出国 留学或工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 369859}, {"id": 347709, "content": "送别父母后，流浪", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1533703}]}